# 15 - Travel Planner
# Create detailed travel itineraries

NAME travel-planner
INPUT destination
INPUT duration DEFAULT "7 days"
INPUT interests DEFAULT "culture, food, nature"
INPUT budget DEFAULT "moderate"

GOAL research "Research $destination focusing on $interests. List top 5-7 attractions and 2-3 neighborhoods. Use existing knowledge; max 1 web search for current info."
GOAL logistics "Plan logistics for $budget budget: 1-2 area recommendations, transport overview. Keep brief."
GOAL itinerary "Create $duration day-by-day itinerary. 2-3 activities per day max. Focus on $interests."
GOAL tips "Add essential tips only: 3-5 key items. Save complete plan to travel-plan-output.md."

RUN plan USING research, logistics, itinerary, tips
